'''薄翅蜻蜓'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Pantala flavescens''}}），俗稱'''黃衣'''，為[[蜻蜓科|蜻蜓科]][[薄翅蜻蜓屬|薄翅蜻蜓屬]]下的一種，廣泛分布於世界[[溫帶|溫帶]]至[[熱帶|熱帶]]地區，為世界上分布最廣的蜻蜓之一<ref>James William Tutt. The Entomologist's Record and Journal of Variation. London: Charles Phipps. 1997:p.213</ref>。

== 辨識特徵 ==
體長約 4 至 5 公分<ref name=Yang2011-1>{{cite book | author = 楊維晟 | title = 賞蟲365天：春夏篇 | publisher = 天下文化 | year = 2011 | url = | isbn = 978-986-216-844-8 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | author = Cynthia Berger | title = Dragonflies | language = de | publisher = Stackpole Books | url =https://archive.org/details/dragonflieswildg00cynt| isbn = 978-0-8117-2971-0 |date=2004年3月}}</ref>，翼展可達 8.4 公分。複眼栗紅色，雙翅透明（也有雙翅呈橄欖色、棕色或黃色，甚至有個體的雙翅呈黑色<ref>{{cite book | author = Ross H. Arnett | title = American Insects:A Handbook of the Insects of America North of Mexico | language =de | publisher = CRC Press | url = | isbn = 978-084-9302-12-1 |date=2000年7月}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = M. J. Samways & R. Osborn | title = Divergence in a transoceanic circumtropical dragonfly on a remote island | journal = Journal of Biogeography | volume = 25 | pages = 935–946 | year = 1998 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-biogeography_1998-09_25_5/page/935}}</ref>）

